ygData.messageBody:
Heh ok well do you have any info on how to get this sword? I play a bard and
a Necro and my bard friend that I group with when on my necro is looking for
this sword. She's level 43 so she should be high enough to complete the
quest or kill the mob.

Naemin Level 5 Wood Elf Bard of E'ci
Naeeldar Level 35 Dark Elf Necromancer of E'ci
